          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The errors of the cross sections include the",
                "statistical errors of the experimental count rates",
                "and several systematical uncertainties."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": 5.0,
                "maximum_value": 10.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error of the charge due to",
                "incomplete charge collection in the Faraday cup was",
                "assumed to be 5% for undegraded beams and 10% for",
                "degraded beams."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainty in the target thickness 10%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-3",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainties due to the solid angle and",
                "the finite beam size may introduce an error of 4%"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-4",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The use of the multispectrumscaling system of",
                "the analyzer introduced an error of 5% in the timing",
                "of the slow-pulsing experiments."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-SYS",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The resulting systematical errors of the",
                "cross sections have values about 20% which are in",
                "most cases larger than the statistical uncertainties.",
                "The relative errors of the isomer ratios are smaller",
                "than those of the cross sections if they are",
                "extracted from the same experiment. In this case,",
                "errors associated with the charge, target thickness",
                "and solid angle cancel."
              ]
            }
          ],
